channel.title: How do i make teles
channel.description: Where do i go to make teles? and how do i? I have the spellbook with all the icons but when i click to tele it doesnt do anything

item.title: How do i make teles
item.dc:creator: @i0wn3v3ry i0wn3v3ry
item.description:
@i0wn3v3ry wrote:

[quote=“usman555, post:3, topic:349079”][quote author=i0wn3v3ry link=topic=445453.msg3270274#msg3270274 date=1279148294]
By learning to follow tuts and not leech.
[/quote]
who in the world of moparscape makes a guide to show how to make teleports?

Ontopic: if you want it as a command, use the triggerTele method or any teleporting method that your server uses (examples are teleportToX, teleportToY, triggerTele, toX, toY)
But if it’s a button, then you either modify a spellbook teleport by going to clickingmost.java and changing the coordinates in the teleport case, or you add one. Adding one is a bit complicated so i suggest to edit one.[/quote]

Google does, alot of people have asked this before.

Ontopic: if you want it as a command, use the triggerTele method or any teleporting method that your server uses (examples are teleportToX, teleportToY, triggerTele, toX, toY)
But if it’s a button, then you either modify a spellbook teleport by going to clickingmost.java and changing the coordinates in the teleport case, or you add one. Adding one is a bit complicated so i suggest to edit one.
